casebody.data:
SIMPSON
v.
Sheriff MCFADDEN, et al No. 194P19 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 24, 2019 David Ezell Simpson, for Simpson, David Ezell. R. Andrew Murray, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

AMENDED ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 23rd of May 2019 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Mecklenburg County:

"Dismissed without prejudice by order of the Court in conference, this the 24th of May 2019."
